283
00:16:53,643 --> 00:16:55,143
Di mana kamar Sumika?

284
00:16:55,143 --> 00:16:56,243
Sebelah sini!

285
00:17:03,843 --> 00:17:05,643
Apa kau baik-baik saja?

286
00:17:07,843 --> 00:17:10,343
Siapa yang melakukan ini padamu?

287
00:17:10,343 --> 00:17:12,943
Wanita merah.

288
00:17:16,843 --> 00:17:18,043
Wanita merah?

289
00:17:18,543 --> 00:17:20,043
Tidak mungkin, bukan?

290
00:17:20,043 --> 00:17:22,943
Kematiannya telah dikonfirmasi.

291
00:17:22,943 --> 00:17:24,543
Tapi...

292
00:17:24,543 --> 00:17:26,243
Setelah mati lampu,

293
00:17:26,243 --> 00:17:29,243
